snippet.title: Auditorium Duet Kickstarter
snippet.description:
The team here at Cipher Prime is gearing up for an epic new project, "Auditorium 2: Duet". This sequel to the award winning game, Auditorium, is going to be bigger, better, and -- most importantly -- it's going be multiplayer! Watch the video, rate it, and check out the Kickstarter page for more info!

http://www.cipherprime.com/kickstarter/
